 Voraussetzung zum Erlernen professioneller Kommunikation und Handlungskompetenz. Das Buch richtet sich in erster Linie an Studierende und Lehrende der Studiengänge zur Sozialen Arbeit.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 70(DE-588)4055676-10(DE-627)1061571590(DE-576)209114959aSozialarbeit2gnd 70(DE-588)4059787-80(DE-627)1061422750(DE-576)209132256aTheorie2gnd 7aEDUCATION / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Politik- u. Sozialwiss. 2005-2012z9783110346817oZDB-23-OPS0 cprintz978348658602240uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348659916940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486599169423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486599169/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OPSc2005d2012